FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__TypedProperty_2) [p].[Id], [p].[AddDate], [p].[BathroomCount], [p].[CityId], [p].[CurrencyId], [p].[Description], [p].[DescriptionDe], [p].[DescriptionRu], [p].[DescriptionTranslateKey], [p].[DistrictId], [p].[Floor], [p].[FloorCount], [p].[GrossArea], [p].[IsActive], [p].[IsFavourite], [p].[IsRent], [p].[IsSold], [p].[NetArea], [p].[Price], [p].[PriceEur], [p].[ProjectDate], [p].[ProjectEndDate], [p].[ProjectNumber], [p].[ProjectStatus], [p].[ProjectTye], [p].[SaloonCount], [p].[SeeClose], [p].[StreetId], [p].[Title], [p].[TitleDe], [p].[TitleRu], [p].[TitleTranslateKey], [p].[TownId], [p].[Year], [p].[ZipCode]
    FROM [Project].[Project] AS [p]
    WHERE ([p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND ([p].[IsActive] = @__TypedProperty_1)
    ORDER BY [p].[AddDate] DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Address].[City] AS [c] ON [t].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Address].[District] AS [d] ON [t].[DistrictId] = [d].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Address].[Street] AS [s] ON [t].[StreetId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Address].[Town] AS [t0] ON [t].[TownId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT @__ImgUrl_0 + [p0].[FileName] AS [c], [p0].[Id], [p0].[ProjectId]
    FROM [ProjectFiles] AS [p0]
    WHERE [p0].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t1] ON ([t].[Id] = [t1].[ProjectId]) AND ([t].[Id] = [t1].[ProjectId])
LEFT JOIN [Feature] AS [f] ON [t].[Id] = [f].[ProjectId]
ORDER BY [t].[AddDate] DESC, [t].[Id], [c].[Id], [d].[Id], [s].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t1].[Id]

SELECT COUNT_BIG(*)
FROM [Project].[Project] AS [p]
